Have fun!

A routine day at the prison. Or so you thought. Rumour is that a prisoner has escaped, find him.
You can lock dangerous prisoners in the Confession Cell located on the lower floor to make sure they dont rebel. 

Terrorists:
Kill the Counter-Terrorist Guards and escape the prison!

Counter-Terrorists:
Arm yourself, these people were locked up for a reason, and now they are trying to escape.
Count up the prisoners and send out search parties to bring back any who have escaped.
Warn the criminals that if you are attacked, you will shoot to kill.

Hi, this map is a very unique jail which is located somewhere in space, there are many fun things to do and executions :
- Space skating, showesrs, borixon says, lab, medic. space knifing ring, deagle for deagle, tower, armory, disco, soccer, pool, cinema, electric chair and few secrets.

If a prisoner tries to run and jump to space he will be teleported to a mini jail which can be opened/closed.

This map`s FPS is not really good but i did put much time to improve it, please dont rate it  on the FPS, i will try to improve it a little bit more in future version.

There are 3 random things that can spawn behind the buttons to open cell, Claws which deal damage, jetpack or a laser knife! Theres 50%50 that anything will spawn.

The map has custom animations and music, thats why the file is so big.

You can improve regeneration in Medic by discovering new cures in the lab.

Map runs ok with about 20 people, as i said before ill try to imrpove it later on.

- In next v i will improve the soccer

Huge thanks to Saitek which made a beautiful job making custom decals for the map!
Also huge thanks goes to mighty pete for his awesome skybox!

This is my first map of any sort, although it's the third release. Brushwork is fairly simple, as would be expected in a jail. My next map will have more detailed brushwork. 

Some notes:

 The four-square/four-corners game is simple to use -- just push the button on top. It randomly selects a square and kills whoever is inside it. 

 The glass hallway is a chicken fight arena. To win, one player must jump on top of (and off of) another player's head. The loser should be killed automatically.

 There is a teleporter which will teleport you randomly to one of sixteen possible destinations. Some are great, others just might kill you...

 Weapons spawn randomly in the cells. One of the cells on the first floor gets a fiveseven, second floor a glock, and third floor a hegrenade. 

 The loser of the race is killed automatically along with whoever else is in the loser's side, so take caution.

 Cells open automatically after 30 seconds and cannot be closed. 

EDIT: Updated version to 3.0a after discovering that the spray contest wall didn't accept sprays. Thanks, XFG.
